{"tid":301643,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"your face your fate？我覺得係your hair your fate","createTime":"2017-06-28T20:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T03:42:03.000Z","uid":63039,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bbe596bbe569577955a2ebae9bac17010370593","tid":301643,"uid":63039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T20:38:38.000Z","msg":"Your face your fate呢一句就聽得多 ，你唔靚仔 就注定你今世命運就係慘情<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/041406_806fae75b60955810233eaf22b1559bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F041406_806fae75b60955810233eaf22b1559bb.jpg&h=4f1ef13e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明白如果你靚仔到陳冠希咁 你咩頭都靚仔，如果你7到八兩金咁 你咩頭都係7<br />\n<br />\n但全香港 有幾多個男仔 靚仔到陳冠希咁同7到八兩金咁先？最多10% 咁其餘90%既中上/中/中下樣呢？<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/042054_0c0c409dd951d3cdacaca8978695103a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F042054_0c0c409dd951d3cdacaca8978695103a.jpg&h=9a3c501c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知你地會講 大佬 你唔靚仔 搞咩頭都哂氣啦<br />\n非也 非也 <br />\n<br />\n一個人既髮型係影響深遠<br />\n<br />\n我比個例子你望下<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/042359_415a6583638e34db802974dafb5f1d96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F042359_415a6583638e34db802974dafb5f1d96.jpg&h=13f75efb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信大家都唔會覺得楊宗緯係靚仔，佢配呢個頭甚至有啲似八兩金，簡單講：中下<br />\n<br />\n但有人幫佢執一執個頭之後<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/042735_29f1b075ed1843c78a5014d3853faec3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F042735_29f1b075ed1843c78a5014d3853faec3.jpg&h=b840891a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知可能明星加埋化妝 係會好睇左，但你夠唔夠膽講佢好睇左 髮型佔既比重唔大？<br />\n<br />\n就算嚴格講佢未到中中 都脫離左中下啦<br />\n<br />\n因為每個人都有合適自己既髮型 有人額高 有人頭髮小 有人頭髮軟 有人頭髮超硬 但只要你搵到岩自己既髮型 你命運就唔係冇得變<br />\n<br />\n如果你係地中海 你可以當冇睇過 同埋我會強烈建議你剷光佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/29/043611_eb74d420a7faa078a1db911a2af168ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2F043611_eb74d420a7faa078a1db911a2af168ed.jpg&h=30b08c89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"551e665470f984ebf78f3864ee1b78db4548e31a","tid":301643,"uid":78595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T21:58:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb3c8a102384947e31302a64f6670f196e9e2a6f","tid":301643,"uid":30724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見你打咁多字又有晒圖咁<br />\n<br />\n成粒鐘都無人入嚟<br />\n<br />\n我幫你推推佢</blockquote><br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc22ce647e21e37d481f63b91a42c516b089ad4","tid":301643,"uid":29473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"男人電髮點睇"},{"pid":"2b0ac94e93e002d05908c910062d7439b5a62017","tid":301643,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人電髮點睇</blockquote><br />\n何解你唔返鄉下問下 d 鄉里？"},{"pid":"34d6338bcc20425783b0c4ea544b95911d136cd6","tid":301643,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"髮型的重要性"}]}